{"parse":{"title":"vine","pageid":53561,"redirects":[],"wikitext":"{{also|Vine|Vīne|viné|vině|víně}}\n==English==\n\n===Etymology===\n{{root|en|ine-pro|*weh₁y-}}\nFrom {{inh|en|enm|vīne}}, from {{der|en|xno|vigne}}, from {{der|en|la-vul|vīnia}}, from {{der|en|la|vīnea|t=vines in a vineyard}}, from {{m|la|vīneus|t=related to wine}}, from {{m|la|vīnum|t=wine}}, from {{der|en|itc-pro|*wīnom}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*wóyh₁nom|t=vine, wine}}, from {{m|ine-pro|*weh₁y-|t=to twist, wrap}}. {{doublet|en|wine}}.\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{IPA|en|/ˈvaɪ̯n/|[ˈvaɪ̯n]}}\n** {{audio|en|en-us-vine.ogg|a=US}}\n* {{rhymes|en|aɪn|s=1}}\n* {{hyph|en|vine}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{en-noun}}\n\n# Any plant whose stem requires support and which climbs by tendrils or twining.\n#: {{syn|en|climber}}\n# Any plant the stem of which creeps along the ground.\n# A stem of such plants, especially when thick and rope-like; a [[liana]].\n#* {{quote-av|en|year=1966|director={{w|Bruce Brown (director)|Bruce Brown}}|title={{w|The Endless Summer}}|text=This was a full-on jungle, full of all kinds of creepy things - snakes, spiders. They expected Tarzan to come swinging by on a '''vine'''.}}\n#* {{quote-book|en|year=1995|author=w:Paul Vautin|title=Turn It Up!|location=Sydney|publisher=Pan Macmillan Australia|page=189|text=I could have easily been in the Congo. Trees, Tarzan-like '''vines''', creepy crawlies, spiders and more spiders.}}\n# {{lb|en|especially|UK}} A [[climbing]] [[plant]] that [[produce]]s [[grape]]s.\n#: {{syn|en|grapevine|winetree}}\n#: {{ux|en|They picked the grapes off the '''vine'''.}}\n#* {{quote-book|en|year=1859|title=[[w:Rubaiyat of Omar Khayyam|The Rub&aacute;iy&aacute;t of Omar Khayy&aacute;m: The Astronomer-Poet of Persia]]|author=w:Edward Fitzgerald|page=2|text=Ir&aacute;m indeed is gone with all its Rose,<br>And Jamsh&yacute;d's Sev'n-ring'd Cup where no one knows;<br>But still the '''Vine''' her ancient Ruby yields,<br>And still a Garden by the Water blows.}}\n# Any plant of the genus {{taxfmt|Vitis|genus}}.\n\n====Hyponyms====\n* {{sense|plant which climbs}} [[liana]]\n* (''vine that climbs by twining, without tendrils''): [[bine]]\n\n====Derived terms====\n{{col4|en\n|{{vern|Alamo vine}} ({{taxlink|Ipomoea dissecta|species}})|{{vern|Alleghany vine}}, {{vern|Allegheny vine}} ({{taxlink|Adlumia fungosa|species}})|American Vine|{{vern|apricot vine}} ({{taxlink|Passiflora incarnata|species}})|[[arbor vine]] ({{taxlink|Merremia tuberosa|species}})\n|[[balloon vine]] ({{taxfmt|Cardiospermum halicacabum|species}})|[[bamboo vine]] ({{taxfmt|Smilax|genus}} spp.)|{{vern|Barbados gooseberry vine}} ({{taxlink|Pereskia aculeata|species}})|{{vern|bean vine}} ({{taxlink|Phaseobus perennis|species}})|{{vern|bell vine}} ({{taxlink|Convolvulus sepium|species}})|{{vern|birdvine}} ({{taxfmt|Loranthus|genus}} spp.)|{{vern|bitter vine}} ({{taxlink|Mikania micrantha|species}})|{{vern|black-eyed Susan vine}} ({{taxlink|Thunbergia alata|species}})|blaspheme-vine,{{vern|blaspheme vine}} ({{taxlink|Smilax laurifolia|species}})|{{vern|blue vine}} ({{taxlink|Ampelanus albidus|species}})|[[bower vine]] ({{taxlink|Pandorea jasminoides|species}})|{{vern|buckwheat vine}} ({{taxfmt|Brunnichia|genus}} spp.)|{{vern|Burdekin vine}} ({{taxlink|Vitis opaca|species}})|vine mesquite\n|[[cacoon vine]] ({{taxlink|Entada rheedei|species}})|{{vern|calabar-bean vine}} ({{taxlink|Physostigma venenosum|species}})|[[calabash vine]] ({{taxfmt|Lagenaria siceraria|species}})|{{vern|canary vine}} ({{taxlink|Adlumia fungosa|species}})|{{vern|canarybird vine}} ({{taxlink|Tropaeolum peregrinum|species}})|{{vern|cantaloupe vine}} ({{taxlink|Cucumis melo cantalupensis|subspecies}})|{{vern|cardinal vine}} ({{taxlink|Ipomoea quamoclit|species}})|{{vern|caustic vine}} ({{taxlink|Sarcostemma australe|species}})|{{vern|chalice vine}} ({{taxlink|Solandra guttata|species}})|chameleon vine|{{vern|Chinese matrimony vine}} ({{taxlink|Lycium chinense|species}})|[[Chinese trumpet vine]] ({{taxfmt|Campsis grandiflora|species}})|[[chocolate vine]] ({{taxlink|Akebia quintata|species}})|[[cinnamon vine]] ({{taxlink|Dioscorea batatas|species}})|{{vern|climbing hemp vine}} ({{taxlink|Mikania scandens|species}})|clinging vine|[[clockvine]], [[clock vine]] ({{taxfmt|Thunbergia|genus}} spp.)|{{vern|common grape vine}} ({{taxfmt|Vitis vinifera|species}})|{{vern|common matrimony vine}} ({{taxfmt|Lycium barbarum|species}}, {{taxlink|Lycium halimifolium|species}})|[[coral vine]] ({{taxlink|Antigonon leptopus|species}}, {{taxlink|Kennedia coccinea|species}})|[[corkscrew vine]] ({{taxlink|Cochliasanthus|genus}} spp.)|{{vern|cow itch vine}} ({{taxlink|Campsis radicans|species}})|{{vern|crab's-eye vine}} ({{taxfmt|Abrus precatorius|species}})|{{vern|cross vine}}, {{l|en|crossvine}}|{{vern|cubeb vine}} ({{taxfmt|Piper cubeba|species}})|{{vern|cucumber vine}} ({{taxfmt|Cucumis sativus|species}})|{{vern|cup-and-saucer vine}} ({{taxlink|Cobaea scandens|species}})|[[cypress vine]] ({{taxlink|Ipomoea quamoclit|species}})|black vine weevil\n|dead on the vine|{{vern|deer vine}} ({{taxfmt|Linnaea borealis|species}})|[[devil's vine]] ({{taxfmt|Epipremnum aureum|species}})|die on the vine|{{vern|dodder vine}} ({{taxfmt|Cuscuta|genus}} spp.)|dwell under one's vine and fig-tree\n|{{vern|Easter lily vine}} ({{taxlink|Beaumontia grandiflora|species}})|{{vern|elephant's-vine}} ({{taxlink|Fockea multiflora|species}})|emerald vine|[[Enslen's vine]] ({{taxlink|Ampelanus albidus|species}})\n|{{vern|flame vine}}, {{vern|flamevine}} ({{taxlink|Pyrostegia ignea|species}})|{{vern|flax vine}} ({{taxlink|Cuscuta epilinum|species}})|{{vern|fleece vine}} ({{taxlink|Polygonum aubertii|species}})\n|garlic vine|[[Goa bean vine]] ({{taxlink|Psophocarpus tetragonolobus|species}})|{{vern|gourd vine}} ({{taxfmt|Cucurbitaceae|family}} spp.)|[[grapevine]], [[grape vine]] ({{taxfmt|Vitis|genus}} spp.)|{{vern|groundnut vine}} ({{taxlink|Apios americana|species}})|{{vern|ground vine}} ({{taxfmt|Linnaea borealis|species}})|{{vern|Guinea gold vine}} ({{taxfmt|Hibbertia|genus}} spp.)\n|{{vern|Harvey's vine}} ({{taxfmt|Bignoniaceae|family}} spp.)|[[headache vine]] ({{taxlink|Clematis glycinoides|species}})|{{vern|hell vine}} ({{taxlink|Campsis radicans|species}})|{{l|en|hemp-vine}}, {{l|en|hempvine}} ({{taxfmt|Mikania|genus}} spp.)|{{vern|hive vine}} ({{taxfmt|Mitchella repens|species}})|[[honeyvine]] ({{taxlink|Cynanchum laeve|species|wplink=0}})|{{vern|hop vine}}, {{l|en|hop-vine}}, {{l|en|hopvine}} ({{taxfmt|Humulus lupulus|species}})|{{vern|Hottentot bread vine}} ({{taxlink|Dioscorea elephantipes|species}})|[[hummingbird vine]] ({{taxlink|Ipomoea quamoclit|species}}; {{taxlink|Campsis radicans|species}})|{{vern|hungry vine}} ({{taxlink|Smilax rotundifolia|species}})\n|{{vern|india-rubber vine}} ({{taxlink|Cryptostegia grandiflora|species}})|{{vern|Isle of Wight vine}} ({{taxfmt|Dioscorea communis|species}})|{{vern|ivy vine}} ({{taxlink|Ampelopsis cordata|species}}; {{taxlink|Parthenocissus quinquefolia|species}})\n|[[jade vine]] ({{taxlink|Strongylodon macrobotrys|species}})\n|[[kangaroo vine]] ({{taxlink|Cissus antarctica|species}})|{{vern|kiwi vine}} ({{taxfmt|Actinidia|genus}} spp.)|[[kudzu vine]] ({{taxfmt|Pueraria|genus}} spp.)\n|{{vern|lace-flower vine}} ({{taxlink|Alsobia dianthiflora|species}}, syn. {{taxlink|Episcia dianthiflora|species}})|[[lawyer vine]] ({{taxfmt|Calamus|genus}} spp. et al.)|{{vern|lemon vine}} ({{taxlink|Pereskia aculeata|species}})|{{vern|licorice vine}} ({{taxfmt|Abrus precatorius|species}})|{{vern|link vine}} ({{taxlink|Vanilla articulata|species}})|love vine\n|{{vern|Madagascar rubber vine}} ({{taxlink|Cryptostegia madagascariensis|species}})|[[Madeira vine]] ({{taxlink|Anredera cordifolia|species}})|[[magnolia vine]] ({{taxfmt|Schisandra|genus}})|[[maidenhair vine]] ({{taxlink|Muehlenbeckia complexa|species}})|[[matrimony vine]], {{l|en|matrimony-vine}} ({{taxfmt|Lycium barbarum|species}})|{{vern|melon vine}} ({{taxfmt|Cucurbitaceae|family}} spp.)|{{vern|Mexican ivy vine}}|{{vern|Mexican vine}} ({{taxlink|Anredera cordifolia|species}})|{{vern|mignonette vine}} ({{taxlink|Anredera cordifolia|species}})|{{vern|mile-a-minute vine}}|{{vern|milk vine}} ({{taxfmt|Marsdenia|genus}} spp.; {{taxlink|Matelia|genus}} spp.)|monkshood vine\n|{{vern|negro vine}} ({{taxlink|Vincetoxicum hirsutum|species}}, {{taxlink|Vincetoxicum negrum|species}})\n|old vines\n|{{vern|partridge-vine}} ({{taxfmt|Mitchella repens|species}})|{{vern|passionflower vine}} ({{taxfmt|Passiflora|genus}} spp.)|{{vern|peanut vine}} ({{taxfmt|Arachis hypogaea|species}})|{{vern|pea vine}}|[[pepper vine]], {{l|en|pepper-vine}} ({{taxlink|Ampelopsis arborea|species}})|{{vern|pipe vine}}, [[pipevine]] ({{taxfmt|Aristolochia|genus}} spp.)|{{vern|poison vine}} ({{taxfmt|Toxicodendron radicans|species}})|[[potato vine]] ({{taxfmt|Solanum tuberosum|species}})|{{vern|prairie gourd vine}} ({{taxlink|Cucurbita foetidissima|species}})|{{vern|pumpkin vine}} ({{taxfmt|Cucurbita pepo|species}})|[[puncture vine]] ({{taxfmt|Tribulus terrestris|species}})\n|{{vern|quarter vine}} ({{taxlink|Bignonia capreolata|species}})\n|{{vern|railroad vine}} ({{taxlink|Ipomea pes-capri|species}})|{{vern|rattan vine}} ({{taxlink|Berchemia scandens|species}})|{{vern|red-bead vine}} ({{taxfmt|Abrus precatorius|species}})|[[rubber vine]] ({{taxlink|Cryptostegia grandiflora|species}})|{{vern|redvine}} ({{taxfmt|Brunnichia|genus}} spp.)|[[Russian vine]] ({{taxlink|Polygonum aubertii|species}})\n|{{vern|sand vine}} ({{taxlink|Ampelanus albidus|species}})|{{vern|scrub vine}} ({{taxlink|Cassytha malantha|species}})|[[seven-year vine]] ({{taxlink|Ipomoea tuberosa|species}})|{{vern|silk vine}} ({{taxlink|Periploca graeca|species}})|[[silver lace vine]], {{vern|silver-lace vine}} ({{taxlink|Polygonum aubertii|species}})|[[silver vine]], [[silvervine]] ({{taxlink|Actinidia polygama|species}}; {{taxlink|Scindapsus pictus|species}})|[[snail vine]] ({{taxlink|Cochliasanthus|genus}} spp.)|snake vine|{{ver